title: U.S. committed to peace between Israel and the Palestinians: Trump
text:
U.S. committed to peace between Israel and the Palestinians: Trump 10:34am EDT - 01:22
U.S. President Donald Trump says he remains committed to peace between Israel and the Palestinians during a recorded message at the opening of the U.S. embassy in Jerusalem.
